-- Ukraine to Increase Naftogaz Ukrainy Capital, RBK Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-02-22T15:36:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-22/ukraine-to-increase-naftogaz-ukrainy-capital-rbk-says.html
Ukraine will raise the statutory
capital of state-managed energy company NAK Naftogaz Ukrainy,
RBK-Ukraine news agency reported, citing Deputy Energy and Coal
Minister Volodymyr Makukha.  The government decided to increase the capital of Naftogaz
by 4 billion hryvnia ($500 million) to 49.84 billion hryvnia,
RBK cited Makukha as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
